'''Bretas超市'''（{{lang-pt|Supermercados Bretas}}）是[[巴西|巴西]]一家大型連鎖[[超市|超市]]，於1954年在[[米納斯吉拉斯州|米納斯吉拉斯州]]成立，目前於[[戈亞斯州|戈亞斯州]]亦設有業務。<ref name="Contexto">{{Cite web |title=Rede varejista implanta grandes investimentos em Anápolis |url=http://www.jornalcontexto.net/noticia_detalhe.php?id_noticia=3180 |accessdate=2020-10-28 |author=Vander Lúcio Barbosa |date=2011-11-19 |publisher=Jornal Contexto |language=pt |archive-date=2014-07-13 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6R2LMpKzq?url=http://www.jornalcontexto.net/noticia_detalhe.php?id_noticia=3180 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite web |title=Sobre Nós |url=https://www.bretas.com.br/sobre-nos/ |accessdate=2020-10-28 |work=Supermercado Bretas |language=pt |archive-date=2020-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128012244/https://www.bretas.com.br/sobre-nos/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 歷史 ==
1950年代，Bretas最初僅在[[米納斯吉拉斯州|米納斯吉拉斯州]][[聖瑪麗亞-迪伊塔比拉|聖瑪麗亞-迪伊塔比拉]]一帶銷售[[咖啡|咖啡]]，於1980年代於[[蒂莫特烏|蒂莫特烏]]設立分公司後開始在巴西境內擴張。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Negociação da rede Bretas agita mercado supermercadista |url=https://www.diariodoaco.com.br/noticia/0029552-negociacao-da-rede-bretas-agita-mercado-supermercadista |accessdate=2020-10-28 |date=2010-09-18 |publisher=Jornal Diário do Aço |language=pt-br |archive-date=2019-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327104004/https://www.diariodoaco.com.br/noticia/0029552-negociacao-da-rede-bretas-agita-mercado-supermercadista |dead-url=no }}</ref>

該超市於2010年代初被[[智利|智利]]跨國零售集團[[桑科薩集團|桑科薩集團]]收購，成為巴西主要的連鎖超市和[[拉丁美洲|拉丁美洲]]較有競爭力的超市之一<ref>{{Cite web |title=Cencosud compra rede de supermercados Bretas |url=http://www.valoronline.com.br/online/cencosud-bretas/49525/323535/cencosud-compra-rede-de-supermercados-bretas |accessdate=2020-10-28 |author=Vanessa Dezem |date=2010-10-15 |publisher=Valor Online |language=pt |archive-date=2014-07-13 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6R2MvMPJk?url=http://www.valor.com.br/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=Supermercado Bretas é vendido para chilenos |url=https://www.otempo.com.br/economia/supermercado-bretas-e-vendido-para-chilenos-1.365870 |accessdate=2020-10-28 |date=2013-04-26 |last=Murta |first=Letícia |work=Economia |language=pt-BR |archive-date=2022-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220205164837/https://www.otempo.com.br/economia/supermercado-bretas-e-vendido-para-chilenos-1.365870 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其在米納斯吉拉斯州和[[戈亞斯州|戈亞斯州]]的部分重要城市設有分店和[[加油站|加油站]]。截至2009年，該超市共有77家分店和12間加油站。<ref name="Contexto"/><ref>{{Cite web |title=Plano Bretas |url=http://www.gironews.com/revistas/revista-153-759.pdf |accessdate=2020-10-28 |author=Pablo Curty |date=2009-06-09 |format=PDF |publisher=Giro News |language=pt |archive-date=2014-07-13 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6R2LZfYTD?url=http://www.gironews.com/revistas/revista-153-759.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>

